  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK448">
<l>iṭippārai yillāta vēmarā maṉṉaṉ</l>
<l>keṭuppā rilāṉuṅ keṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The king, who is without the guard of men who can rebuke him, will perish, even though there be no one to destroy him.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
